summary: A save game right before you build your character and name them, with all perks and all skills set to 9999 carry weight 9999 all spells/shouts and a good sum of money - ok it was a good idea but if you pick anything but nord it sets all the stats back to normal, you do however keep the gold, perks, spells and shouts
descriptionHtml:
A save game right before you build your character and name them, with all perks and all skills set to 9999 carry weight 9999 all spells/shouts and a good sum of money

Basically if you don\'t know how to use the console or if you don\'t want to enter all 250 some perks yourself here :)

  - ok it was a good idea but if you pick anything but nord it sets all the stats back to normal, you do however keep the gold, perks, spells and shouts
